data.description: NEW ROOF!!! Introducing, this stunning four-bedroom, two-bathroom home located in a fantastic neighborhood of Splawn Ranch! This home offers a perfect blend of convenience and modern comfort. Built-in 2008, this beautiful home has 2055 sq. ft. of living space and modern luxuries, you wont want to miss! The inviting and warm floor plan leaves you feeling right at home, with ample space for relaxing and entertaining!  Enjoy a stylish interior coupled with serene outdoor living spaces in which to unwind. Do not miss out on this fantastic opportunity to own your dream home!
